import React, { useState } from "react"

import { NavLink } from "react-router-dom"
import {
  MDBContainer,
  MDBNavbar,
  MDBNavbarBrand,
  MDBNavbarToggler,
  MDBNavbarNav,
  MDBNavbarItem,
  MDBIcon,
  MDBCollapse,
} from "mdb-react-ui-kit"

export default function App() {
  const [showNavSecond, setShowNavSecond] = useState(false)

  return (
    <>
      <MDBNavbar
        expand="sm"
        light
        bgColor="light"
        className="fixed-top"
        style={{ zIndex: "1000" }}
      >
        <MDBContainer>
          <MDBNavbarBrand tag="div">Tik Games</MDBNavbarBrand>
          <MDBNavbarToggler
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-label="Toggle navigation"
            onClick={() => setShowNavSecond(!showNavSecond)}
          >
            <MDBIcon icon="bars" fas />
          </MDBNavbarToggler>
          <MDBCollapse navbar show={showNavSecond}>
            <MDBNavbarNav>
              <NavLink end to="/" className="nav-link" activeclassname="active">
                Trang chủ
              </NavLink>
              <NavLink
                to="/question-and-answer"
                className="nav-link"
                activeclassname="active"
              >
                Hướng dẫn
              </NavLink>
              <MDBNavbarItem>
                <NavLink
                  to="/pricing"
                  className="nav-link"
                  activeclassname="active"
                >
                  Bảng giá
                </NavLink>
              </MDBNavbarItem>
            </MDBNavbarNav>
          </MDBCollapse>
        </MDBContainer>
      </MDBNavbar>
    </>
  )
}
